flowchart Treasure Hunt
direction-tb

[Start]  Receive a treasure map
{Read}   Can you read the map?
[Decode] Decode the cipher
[Sail]   Set sail for the island
{Found}  Found the X?
[Search] Search the next cove
[Dig]    Dig for the chest
[Loot]   Haul the loot aboard

(Start) -> (Read)
(Read) -No-> (Decode)
(Decode) -> (Sail)
(Read) -Yes-> (Sail)
(Sail) -> (Found)
(Found) -No-> (Search)
(Search) -> (Found)
(Found) -Yes-> (Dig)
(Dig) -> (Loot)
